---
import me from "@assets/me.jpg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Heading from "@components/Heading.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title='Home'>
  <section class='w-screen h-screen flex justify-center items-center'>
    <div class='flex flex-col gap-4'>
      <h1 class='text-center text-7xl font-black md:text-8xl'>Neville Brem</h1>
      <h3 class='mx-auto font-semibold italic text-xl md:text-2xl'>
        Bringing{" "}
        <span
          class='font-extrabold text-primary duration-200 ease-in-out hover:tracking-widest hover:text-green-500'
        >
          life
        </span>{" "}
        to every page
      </h3>
      <a href='#about' class='btn btn-primary mx-auto text-white font-bold'>
        Explore
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id='about' class='max-w-5xl mx-auto'>
    <div
      class='mx-8 flex grid-cols-2 flex-col-reverse gap-16 py-8 md:grid md:gap-0'
    >
      <div class='m-auto'>
        <h1 class='text-xl md:text-3xl font-black'>About me</h1>
        <p class='mt-2 text-balance'>
          Hey there, my name is Neville Brem and I am a Web Developer from
          Zurich, Switzerland. I love coding, computer science and everything to
          do with tech. I am 16 years old in a High School in Zurich. I began my
          coding journey in 2021. Since then I've been fascinated with web
          development and learned many technologies around it. I have passions
          for all things digital including photography, editing and AI.
        </p>
      </div>
      <Image
        src={me}
        alt='me:)'
        quality='mid'
        loading='lazy'
        class='my-auto ml-auto mr-auto w-3/4 md:mr-0 border-2 border-base-300 rounded-box duration-200 hover:shadow-lg shadow-sm'
      />
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    id='information'
    class='grid-row-3 md:mx-auto flex grid-cols-3 flex-col gap-8 py-8 md:grid max-w-7xl mx-8'
  >
    <div class='bento-box flex justify-center'>
      <div class='my-auto'>
        <h1
          class='bento-heading bg-gradient-to-bl from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-6xl text-transparent'
        >
          3 Years
        </h1>
        <p>Of experience</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='bento-box col-span-2'>
      <h1
        class='bento-heading bg-gradient-to-bl from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-6xl text-transparent md:text-8xl'
      >
        1K+
      </h1>
      <p>
        Contributions on{" "}
        <a href='https://github.com/nevthereal' target='_blank' class='anchor'>
          GitHub
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class='bento-box col-span-2 flex flex-col'>
      <div class='m-auto'>
        <h1
          class='bento-heading bg-gradient-to-bl from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-4xl text-transparent md:text-6xl'
        >
          Why me?
        </h1>
        <ul
          class='list-inside list-decimal text-lg font-semibold md:text-xl text-left'
        >
          <li>Beautifully crafted Websites</li>
          <li>Modern Design</li>
          <li>Keen eye on detail</li>
          <li>Fast response times</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='bento-box bg-gradient-to-b from-white/50 to-orange-500/50'>
      <h1 class='bento-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl text-white'>Stack:</h1>
      <ul class='font-bold text-2xl text-white'>
        <li>
          <a href='https://kit.svelte.dev' target='_blank'> SvelteKit </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='https://astro.build' target='_blank'> Astro </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='https://tailwindcss.com' target='_blank'> Tailwind </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='https://orm.drizzle.team' target='_blank'> Drizzle </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='https://neon.tech' target='_blank'> Neon </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='https://lucia-auth.com'>Lucia</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class='col-span-3 flex grid-cols-2 flex-col gap-8 md:grid'>
      <div class='bento-box flex'>
        <div class='mx-auto flex flex-col text-left'>
          <i
            class='fa-solid fa-quote-left mx-auto bg-gradient-to-bl from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-left text-3xl text-transparent'
          ></i>
          <p class='text-center text-2xl font-semibold italic'>
            Design is not just what it looks like and feels like. Design is how
            it works. <br />
            <span class='text-lg font-normal'>- Steve Jobs</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='bento-box flex items-center justify-center'>
        <div>
          <h1
            class='bento-heading bg-gradient-to-bl from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-4xl text-transparent duration-200 ease-in-out hover:tracking-widest'
          >
            Interactivity
          </h1>
          <p>
            Creates a feeling of{" "}
            <span class='group font-bold'>
              connection{" "}
              <a
                href='https://github.com/nevthereal/nevillebrem-astro'
                target='_blank'
                class='hidden group-hover:inline'
              >
                <i class='fa-solid fa-link'></i>
              </a>
            </span>{" "}
            to the site.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id='timeline' class='max-w-5xl md:mx-auto mx-8 prose-a:link'>
    <Heading title='My timeline' subtitle='A little bit of history' />
    <ul
      class='timeline timeline-snap-icon max-md:timeline-compact timeline-vertical mb-16'
    >
      <li>
        <div class='timeline-middle'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-check-circle'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='timeline-start mb-10 md:text-end'>
          <time class='font-mono italic'>Early 2022</time>
          <div class='text-lg font-black'>First contact</div>
          Learned HTML and CSS in School. This was my first contact with Web Development
          and would change my life for the better.
        </div>
        <hr />
      </li>
      <li>
        <hr />
        <div class='timeline-middle'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-check-circle'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='timeline-end mb-10'>
          <time class='font-mono italic'>July 2022</time>
          <div class='text-lg font-black'>Early Contributor</div>
          Discovered GitHub and created my first
          <a
            href='https://github.com/nevthereal/TheCreators'
            target='_blank'
            class='anchor'>Repository</a
          >. I was still building in vanilla HTML and CSS (and rocked
          animations) but was too scared to learn JavaScript.
        </div>
        <hr />
      </li>
      <li>
        <hr />
        <div class='timeline-middle'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-check-circle'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='timeline-start mb-10 md:text-end'>
          <time class='font-mono italic'>Summer 2022</time>
          <div class='text-lg font-black'>Discovering React & Tailwind</div>
          Got into React and built my first
          <a
            href='https://github.com/nevthereal/portfolio-react'
            target='_blank'
            class='anchor'>Portfolio.</a
          >
          I also discovered Tailwind and began one of my biggest projects:
          <a href='https://wolffebricks.rocks' target='_blank' class='anchor'
            >Will's Brix</a
          >, now known as Wolffe Bricks.
        </div>
        <hr />
      </li>
      <li>
        <hr />
        <div class='timeline-middle'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-check-circle'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='timeline-end mb-10'>
          <time class='font-mono italic'>Summer 2023</time>
          <div class='text-lg font-black'>Fresh start</div>
          After a long break of coding, I call it the coding winter, I got back into
          development. Rebranded Wolffe Bricks and rebuilt the website with Stripe
          and built a backend in expressjs. Later I discovered TypeScript and built
          my
          <a href='https://barmates.ch' target='_blank' class='anchor'
            >favorite landing page</a
          > utilising framer-
        </div>
        <hr />
      </li>
      <li>
        <hr />
        <div class='timeline-middle'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-check-circle'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='timeline-start mb-10 md:text-end'>
          <time class='font-mono italic'>Fall 2023</time>
          <div class='text-lg font-black'>SvelteKit</div>
          Discovered SvelteKit and built some first applications with it. This made
          me pick up on web dev again and made me a full stack dev. I rebuilt
          <a href='https://wolffebricks.rocks' class='anchor'>Wolffe Bricks</a> with
          it and loved the DX. And the <i>vibes</i>.
        </div>
        <hr />
      </li>
      <li>
        <hr />
        <div class='timeline-middle'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-check-circle'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='timeline-end mb-10 md:text-start'>
          <time class='font-mono italic'>Early 2024</time>
          <div class='text-lg font-black'>Houston and YouTube</div>
          I learned Astro for more content-driven and static pages like landing pages.
          I also began my
          <a
            href='https://youtube.com/@nevillebrem'
            target='_blank'
            class='anchor'>YouTube channel</a
          >.
        </div>
        <hr />
      </li>
      <li>
        <hr />
        <div class='timeline-middle'>
          <i class='fa-solid fa-check-circle'></i>
        </div>
        <div class='timeline-start mb-10 md:text-end'>
          <time class='font-mono italic'>Summer 2024</time>
          <div class='text-lg font-black'>Holy sh*t</div>
          I would start and call myself a kind of experienced developer. I discovered
          many technologies, settled with some cool stuff, worked with DBs, AI and
          had an extensive relationship with <a
            href='https://superforms.rocks'
            target='_blank'>Forms</a
          >. I am keeping up with productivity, building <a
            href='https://zenithproductivity.app'>Zenith</a
          >, my most advanced project yet.
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
